column2: Cohen & Steers Select Preferred and Income Fund Inc

Cohen & Steers Select Preferred and Income Fund, Inc. (the Fund) is a closed-end management investment company. The Fund invests in securities that are listed on the New York Stock Exchange (NYSE). It also invests in preferred securities, corporate bonds, short-term investments, interest rate swap contracts and forward foreign currency exchange contracts. The Fund invests at least 25% of its net assets in the financial sector. It invests in various sectors, such as electric, real estate, industrials, utilities, other, insurance, banks, material and pipelines. Its portfolio has investment in geographic region, including the United States, the United Kingdom, France, Switzerland, Japan, the Netherlands, Bermuda, Hong Kong, Italy and Spain.
